<section xmlns:ns1="http://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codified" xmlns:ns0="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <num>8-107.03</num>
  <heading>Seller’s burden in civil action.</heading>
  <text>Concerning a civil action against the seller for injuries resulting from violations of this subchapter, a seller has the burden of proving that the cleaning agent complies with § <cite path="§8-107.02">8-107.02</cite>.</text>
